# -*-perl-*-

=head1 NAME

QUICK_LOOK_TEST - Basic recipe to co-add and display DREAM/Stare images

=head1 DESCRIPTION

Basic processing recipe suitable for DREAM/STARE images.

=head1 KNOWN ISSUES

This primitive can not handle time series observing modes.

